The terms and conditions in relation to digital products and bill payments set out below are applicable to and binding on You in conjunction with these SSOID terms and conditions. Each SSOID term or condition is applicable to and binding on You, for any of Your activities on the Paytm Platform, even if such term or condition is not specifically reproduced herein below.
